data.oai_dc:dc: These data provide the information on the number of fry of each genotype collected each day from each aquarium. Group is referred to as aquarium in the paper, number of fry refers to how many fry of each type were collected, pctredsires is the %red male category of which there are five types (25%, 33$, 50%, 66%, and 75%, frytype is either red or wild-type, collection refers to the number of days that data were collected for each group
